These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, grey, amber, orange
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person who likes lilac##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
7. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Color         | grey | orange    | amber      | lilac |
| Transport   | bike   | subway | snowmobile | van        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, guinea-pig, goldfish, hamster
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | goldfish | hamster | rabbit |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, baseball, climbing, basketball
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing | singing | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Sport   | swimming | climbing    | basketball | baseball    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy, dahlia, rose
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the freelancer is the person driving the train##1
2. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Flower       | poppy     | rose      | daffodil     | dahlia      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

