.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, orchid, poppy, rose
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the person who growsdaffodil is the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person who growspoppy##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person who growsrose is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Flower           | orchid | poppy | rose | daffodil |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | folk     | reggae | funk       |

