.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, nurse, software-developer, librarian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, drama, mystery
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, french, nigerian, pakistani
1. the nurse is the nigerian##1
2. the pakistani is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the librarian is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
6. the pakistani is the software-developer##1
7. the french is on the left of the pakistani##1
8. the nurse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job      | librarian | software-developer     | engineer | nurse |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | animation | drama       | crime    |
| Nationality   | french   | pakistani | canadian    | nigerian |

