The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, electronic, funk, punk
4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, whist, scrabble
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the bartender is the fan of electronic##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
4. the fan of funk is the person playing snooker##1
5. the lawyer is on the far left##1
6. the scientist is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
7. the person playing whist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job           | lawyer  | architect | bartender  | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | d&b       | electronic | punk      |
| Game   | snooker | canasta  | scrabble    | whist    |

